@startuml seq_18_hide_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-18 Hide Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Hide Repo" as HideRepo

User -> Frontend: Click "Hide Post"
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/posts/{id}/hide
Controller -> Service: Hide Post (userID, postID)
Service -> PostRepo: Verify post exists and is visible
PostRepo --> Service: Post is valid

Service -> HideRepo: Create hidden-post record
HideRepo --> Service: Record created
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Remove post from current feed view
@enduml